ph-transit-graph-api

> Community-driven route and fare data API for Philippine transit.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
STACK
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Spring Boot 3.5
Spring Data JPA + Hibernate
PostgreSQL 16
Maven
Lombok
Bean Validation
Spring Security + JWT

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GETTING STARTED
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites
- Java 21+
- PostgreSQL
- Maven
Setup
  git clone https://github.com/kuwarte/ph-transit-graph-api.git
  cd ph-transit-graph-api
  cp .env.example .env
  mvn spring-boot:run
Database
  CREATE DATABASE ph_transit_graph;
  CREATE USER transituser WITH PASSWORD 'yourpassword';
  GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON DATABASE ph_transit_graph TO transituser;
  GRANT ALL ON SCHEMA public TO transituser;
Environment variables (.env)
  APP_NAME=ph-transit-graph
  DB_URL=jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/ph_transit_graph
  DB_USERNAME=transituser
  DB_PASSWORD=yourpassword
  JWT_SECRET=your-base64-secret
  JWT_EXPIRATION=86400000

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
AUTHENTICATION
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Protected endpoints require a Bearer token in the Authorization header.
  Authorization: Bearer <token>
Roles
  COMMUTER  → saved routes, submit reports
  OPERATOR  → manage own routes, stops, fares
  ADMIN     → verify operators, manage reports, platform analytics

----------------------------------------------------------------------------
API ENDPOINTS
----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Base URL: http://localhost:8080/api/v1

Legend
  [PUBLIC]   no auth required
  [AUTH]     any authenticated user
  [OPERATOR] requires OPERATOR role
  [ADMIN]    requires ADMIN role

Auth
  POST   /auth/register               [PUBLIC]
  POST   /auth/register/operator      [PUBLIC]
  POST   /auth/login                  [PUBLIC]
  GET    /auth/me                     [AUTH]

Places
  GET    /places                      [PUBLIC]
  GET    /places/{id}                 [PUBLIC]
  GET    /places/search?municipality=&province=  [PUBLIC]
  POST   /places                      [ADMIN]
  PUT    /places/{id}                 [ADMIN]
  DELETE /places/{id}                 [ADMIN]

Routes
  GET    /routes                      [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/{id}                 [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/search?origin=&destination=     [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/vehicle/{type}       [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/code/{routeCode}     [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/my-routes            [OPERATOR]
  POST   /routes                      [OPERATOR]
  PUT    /routes/{id}                 [OPERATOR]
  PATCH  /routes/{id}/status          [ADMIN]
  DELETE /routes/{id}                 [OPERATOR]

Stops
  GET    /routes/{routeId}/stops                 [PUBLIC]
  GET    /routes/{routeId}/stops/{stopId}        [PUBLIC]
  POST   /routes/{routeId}/stops                 [OPERATOR]
  PUT    /routes/{routeId}/stops/{stopId}        [OPERATOR]
  PATCH  /routes/{routeId}/stops/reorder         [OPERATOR]
  DELETE /routes/{routeId}/stops/{stopId}        [OPERATOR]

Fares
  GET    /routes/{routeId}/fares                 [PUBLIC]
  GET    /fares/calculate?from=&to=              [PUBLIC]
  POST   /routes/{routeId}/fares                 [OPERATOR]
  PUT    /routes/{routeId}/fares/{fareId}        [OPERATOR]
  DELETE /routes/{routeId}/fares/{fareId}        [OPERATOR]

Operators
  GET    /operators                   [PUBLIC]
  GET    /operators/{id}              [PUBLIC]
  GET    /operators/{id}/routes       [PUBLIC]
  GET    /operators/pending           [ADMIN]
  PUT    /operators/profile           [OPERATOR]
  PATCH  /operators/{id}/verify       [ADMIN]

Reports
  GET    /reports                     [ADMIN]
  GET    /reports/{id}                [ADMIN]
  GET    /reports/my-reports          [AUTH]
  POST   /reports                     [AUTH]
  PATCH  /reports/{id}/approve        [ADMIN]
  PATCH  /reports/{id}/reject         [ADMIN]

Commuter
  GET    /commuter/saved-routes             [AUTH]
  POST   /commuter/saved-routes/{routeId}   [AUTH]
  DELETE /commuter/saved-routes/{routeId}   [AUTH]

Admin
  GET    /admin/users                 [ADMIN]
  GET    /admin/users/{id}            [ADMIN]
  PATCH  /admin/users/{id}/deactivate [ADMIN]
  GET    /admin/analytics             [ADMIN]

